snippet.title: Outpath: First Journey Steam Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Outpath: First Journey is a prologue chapter of the main game, Outpath. An experimental clicker base building game. Craft, gather & manage resources, build your base and buy more islands to exploit and expand!

Try the free prologue:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2237980/Outpath_First_Journey/

Wishlist the full game
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2237970/Outpath
